
     Amiga Link is an incredible online Amiga magazine!  It has all the
newest news, reviews of software and hardware (including games...we believe
in having fun on your Amiga too) and opinion pieces!  You can find Amiga
Link on all good Amiga BBSs, in the docs/mags directory of Aminet, and on
many WWW pages, including the Amiga home page.  

     You can also subscribe to Amiga Link by e-mailing
<amigalink-request@ramiga.cts.com> with the message: 
ADD <your e-mail address>


               Joshua Galun
           Editor of Amiga Link